arguments.template:
<ng-container *ngIf="options; else noOptions">
  <m4-checkbox *ngFor="let option of options | objectKeys" [value]="options[option]" [caption]="option"></m4-checkbox>
</ng-container>
<ng-template #noOptions>
  <ng-content></ng-content>
</ng-template>

<ng-container *ngIf="options; else noOptions">
  <m4-radio *ngFor="let option of options | objectKeys" [value]="options[option]"
            [caption]="option" [name]="name"></m4-radio>
</ng-container>
<ng-template #noOptions>
  <ng-content></ng-content>
</ng-template>

arguments.template:
<select #input [multiple]="multiple"


        [attr.data-prepend]="prepend"
        [attr.data-duration]="duration"
        [attr.data-append]="append"
        [attr.data-drop-height]="dropHeight"
        [attr.data-filter]="filter"
        [attr.data-filter-placeholder]="filterPlaceholder"

        [attr.data-cls-select]="clsSelect"
        [attr.data-cls-prepend]="clsPrepend"
        [attr.data-cls-append]="clsAppend"
        [attr.data-cls-option]="clsOption"
        [attr.data-cls-option-group]="clsOptionGroup"
        [attr.data-cls-drop-list]="clsDropList"
        [attr.data-cls-selected-item]="clsSelectedItem"
        [attr.data-cls-selected-item-remover]="clsSelectedItemRemover">

  <ng-content *ngIf="!options"></ng-content>

  <ng-container *ngIf="options | isArray">
    <ng-container *ngFor="let option of options">
      <option *ngIf="!option.options" [value]="option.value | createHash" [attr.data-template]="option.dataTemplate">
        {{option.title}}
      </option>

      <optgroup *ngIf="option.options" [label]="option.groupName">
        <option *ngFor="let childOption of option.options" [value]="childOption.value | createHash" [attr.data-template]="childOption.dataTemplate">
          {{childOption.title}}
        </option>
      </optgroup>
    </ng-container>
  </ng-container>
</select>
